.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, mango, onion, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, october, january
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indonesian, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the australian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the australian##7
 8. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
11. the chinese is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apricot   | onion       | watermelon    | mango      |
| Birthday   | february | january | may         | october   |
| Nationality   | italian   | australian  | chinese       | indonesian |
| Sport         | golf      | volleyball  | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

