 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 5. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 8. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the japanese##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is the italian##1
11. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating spinach and the owner of the lizard##2
12. the owner of the chinchilla is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |      4      |
