 4. the person watching superhero movies is the entrepreneur##1
 5. the scientist is not the person watching comedy movies##6
 6. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is not the owner of the dog##6
 9. the doctor is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the snake is not the person watching adventure movies##6
13. the fisherman is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the owner of the turtle##7
14. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4

